descript.abstract:
Urban agglomerations in 2000 © 2005 Richard LeGates. Created from data in United Nations Department of Economic and Social Affairs, Population Division Urban Agglomerations 2003 © 2000 United Nations.
This data accompanies exercise 1 in Richard LeGates, Think Globally, Act Regionally (Redlands: ESRI Press, 2005) copyright © 2005 ESRI. The data in this exercise was created from sources described in this metadata and more fully documented in the data credits in Think Globally, Act Regionally.
Exercise 1 contains data on the location and estimated population size of the most populous cities in the world in 1800, 1850, 1900, and 2000 and the location of global cities in 2000.
